{"id":5103,"date":"2025-02-24T09:50:11","date_gmt":"2025-02-24T09:50:11","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/?p=5103"},"modified":"2025-06-18T05:34:44","modified_gmt":"2025-06-18T05:34:44","slug":"announcing-our-new-website","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/agency-news\/announcing-our-new-website\/","title":{"rendered":"Announcing Our New Website &amp; Brand Evolution"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Our new website is finally here! After months of work,&nbsp;we\u2019re excited to reveal the brand new <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/\"><strong>CreativeWeb<\/strong> website<\/a>!&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>It&#8217;s complete with a fresh new look, an evolved &amp; improved brand identity, as well as a showcase of our latest, award-winning projects.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Like many agencies, our own site took a backseat while we focused on developing cutting-edge websites for our clients. But this update was long overdue! It&#8217;s more than just a redesign, it marks a brand evolution, a refined identity that better reflects who we are today and where we\u2019re headed next.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-1 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"767\" src=\"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_Home-1024x767.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9028\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_Home-1024x767.webp 1024w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_Home-300x225.webp 300w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_Home-768x576.webp 768w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_Home-1536x1151.webp 1536w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_Home-576x432.webp 576w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_Home-1366x1024.webp 1366w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_Home-1600x1199.webp 1600w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_Home.webp 1812w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"758\" src=\"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_Team-edited-1024x758.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9027\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_Team-edited-1024x758.webp 1024w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_Team-edited-300x222.webp 300w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_Team-edited-768x569.webp 768w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_Team-edited-1536x1137.webp 1536w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_Team-edited-576x427.webp 576w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_Team-edited-1366x1012.webp 1366w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_Team-edited-1600x1185.webp 1600w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_Team-edited.webp 1769w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<br>\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-our-brand-evolution-a-fresh-yet-familiar-look\">Our Brand Evolution: A Fresh Yet Familiar Look<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Our brand has always been about pushing creative boundaries while maintaining a strong foundation of technical excellence. With this refresh, we\u2019ve made subtle yet impactful refinements to our visual identity, from modernised typography and colour tweaks to a cleaner and more sophisticated aesthetic.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Rather than a radical change, this refresh fine-tunes our visual identity while keeping us instantly recognisable. And this is just the beginning\u2026 you can expect more updates later this year as we continue to evolve.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-2 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-style-default\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"716\" src=\"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_SEOChecker-article-1024x716.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9026\" style=\"object-fit:cover\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_SEOChecker-article-1024x716.webp 1024w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_SEOChecker-article-300x210.webp 300w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_SEOChecker-article-768x537.webp 768w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_SEOChecker-article-1536x1074.webp 1536w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_SEOChecker-article-576x403.webp 576w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_SEOChecker-article-1366x955.webp 1366w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_SEOChecker-article-1600x1118.webp 1600w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_SEOChecker-article.webp 1777w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Why not try out our new <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/seo-checker-analysis-tool\/\">SEO Checker<\/a><\/strong>? (It&#8217;s Free!)<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"716\" src=\"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_Map-article-1024x716.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9029\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_Map-article-1024x716.webp 1024w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_Map-article-300x210.webp 300w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_Map-article-768x537.webp 768w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_Map-article-1536x1074.webp 1536w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_Map-article-576x403.webp 576w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_Map-article-1366x955.webp 1366w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_Map-article-1600x1118.webp 1600w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_Map-article.webp 1777w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>The interactive map showcases just a handful of our clients from around the globe<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-what-s-new-on-our-website\">What\u2019s New on Our Website?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We didn\u2019t just want to give our site a new lick of paint but rather reimagine the whole experience. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here\u2019s what you\u2019ll now find on our site:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Updated Projects:<\/strong> Our portfolio now showcases some of the most exciting projects we\u2019ve worked on in the past couple of years, including award-winning web designs and client success stories.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Expanded Services:<\/strong> We\u2019ve introduced new offerings, including our <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/website-audit\/\">Website Audit Service<\/a>, designed to give businesses the insights they need to optimise their digital presence.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Improved User Experience:<\/strong> From smooth animations and interactive elements to 3JS-powered effects, the new site shows the creative and technical direction we\u2019ve taken with our projects, with being highly engaging, visually stunning, and performance-driven.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"766\" src=\"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_Portfolio-1024x766.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9031\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_Portfolio-1024x766.webp 1024w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_Portfolio-300x225.webp 300w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_Portfolio-768x575.webp 768w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_Portfolio-1536x1149.webp 1536w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_Portfolio-576x431.webp 576w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_Portfolio-1366x1022.webp 1366w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_Portfolio-1600x1197.webp 1600w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_Portfolio.webp 1804w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Our new <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/portfolio\/\">Portfolio<\/a><\/strong> section showcases our best and latest projects<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"597\" src=\"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_WebsiteAudit-1024x597.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9032\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_WebsiteAudit-1024x597.webp 1024w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_WebsiteAudit-300x175.webp 300w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_WebsiteAudit-768x447.webp 768w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_WebsiteAudit-1536x895.webp 1536w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_WebsiteAudit-576x336.webp 576w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_WebsiteAudit-1366x796.webp 1366w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_WebsiteAudit-1600x932.webp 1600w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_WebsiteAudit.webp 1816w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Our <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/website-audit\/\">Website Audit<\/a><\/strong> service is perfect for helping you understand how your website can be improved<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-our-focus-moving-forward\">Our Focus Moving Forward<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This update demonstrates our ongoing commitment to innovation and growth. Here\u2019s what you can expect going forward:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>More frequent updates:<\/strong> Get ready for more insights, case studies, and behind-the-scenes content as we ramp up our marketing efforts.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Ongoing website improvements:<\/strong> We\u2019ll keep improving and evolving the website, making sure it stays up-to-date with the times.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Pushing creative boundaries:<\/strong> Our portfolio will continue expanding with cutting-edge designs, pushing boundaries. <\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-this-is-just-the-beginning\">This is Just the Beginning<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>After having finally carved out some time to refresh our website, bringing it up to date with our latest work and demonstrating our evolving approach to design; We feel this update reflects not just what we\u2019ve been working on, but how we\u2019ve been pushing boundaries through incorporating 3D elements using Spline and Three.js to create more immersive, interactive experiences. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote is-layout-flow wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow\">\n<p>It\u2019s been a long time coming, and we\u2019re looking forward to sharing more of what we\u2019ve been up to in the months to come.<\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n\n\n\n<p>While you\u2019re here, explore the new site, check out our latest projects, and let us know what you think!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"765\" src=\"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_CostCalculator-edited-1024x765.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_CostCalculator-edited-1024x765.webp 1024w, https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/Screenshot_CostCalculator-edited-300x